## üîë Important Shortcuts (Path Aliases)

In [vite.config.ts](file:///c:/Projects/Finance-Tracker-fe/vite.config.ts), we have shortcuts:

```typescript
alias: {
  '@app': './src/app',
  '@pages': './src/pages',
  '@widgets': './src/widgets',
  '@features': './src/features',
  '@entities': './src/entities',
  '@shared': './src/shared',
}
```

**What this means:**
- Instead of: `import Button from '../../shared/ui/Button/Button'`
- You write: `import Button from '@shared/ui/Button/Button'`

It's like **speed dial** for your phone - instead of typing the full number, you press one button!

